# NIX STORE
Nixpkgs: nixpkgs.nix
Source: https://github.com/NixOS/nix
Description: Manage the Nix store (integrity, GC, repair).
Version: nix --version

## Commands

### Basics
- nix store gc: Run the garbage collector to free disk space.

### Essentials
- nix store verify: Check the store for missing or corrupted paths.
- nix store optimize: Deduplicate identical files in the store.

### Intermediaries
- nix store repair: Fix corrupted paths.

## Tips
- Run 'nix store optimize' periodically to save space.

